title: MOTIVERSITY - BEST OF 2020
itunes:title: MOTIVERSITY - BEST OF 2020
itunes:subtitle: Motiversity
description:
MOTIVERSITY'S BEST SPEECHES OF 2020! These are some of our Best Motivational Speech Videos of the year! It's been a crazy year but we've been here every step of the way through it so we're taking a look back at our most epic inspirational speeches and we compiled them into one giant hour-long motivational speech. From everyone at Motiversity, the team, all of the speakers, and myself, thank you so much for all of your support this year!

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
